Lagos – A female passenger has been given the beating of her life by an angry Uber driver in Lagos An Uber driver has been spotted in a viral video assaulting a female passenger with a whip for allegedly questioning him during a trip to Ikeja area of Lagos.  Narrating the incident, a Twitter user @eziinneee said the Uber driver tried to park at a flooded area where they couldn’t alight from. However the driver who drove out from the flooded spot allegedly flared up after her friend who wasn’t paying attention during the trip asked why he was “driving quite far when they already said they will walk”. Watch the video below: #Uber driver assaults his female passenger with a whip in Ikeja, #Lagos A post shared by  Lindaikejiblog (@lindaikejiblogofficial) on Sep 13, 2019 at 1:05am PDT Source